title: Immortal Weapons 01-05 (2009|Digital|AnHeroGold-Empire)
description:
This limited series ties into the Immortal Iron Fist run by Brubaker and Fraction, and features Fat Cobra in his own little humorous side story. Written by Duane Swierczynski and Jason Aaron with art by Travel Foreman and Mico Suayan. Promotional info for the collected edition - "Fat Cobra! No man has fought more heartily, consumed more mightily, or lived life more fully! Fat Cobra! Master of the sumo thunder stomp and the devil's skullcrusher! Fat Cobra! Immortal Weapon from the Seven Capital Cities of Heaven! But to this day, no man has known the story of Fat cobra's life...including the Cobra himself! Discover the shocking origins of this boisterous brawler and witness his decades of adventure! Meanwhile, Danny Rand embarks on his own mission of search and adventure."

These are the low-res digital webrips by AnPymHero-Empire, still quite clean though. Thanks to them for their work, please seed and enjoy! :-)
